wikipedia_page.main:
James Price (born 27 October 1981) is an English footballer who played at the right or centre of defence for Scarborough Athletic, in the Northern Premier League Division One North. Price has made over 150 appearances in the Football League and Football Conference.
As of 2021, he plays for and captains Emley in the Northern Counties East league Premier Division
